The tl;dr is that this game is more than worth its dollar-value cost

reviewText:
I recommend you to play this game if:

- You want to switch on your brain to unravel a story;
- You like to interpret facts in multiple ways and watch the things from different perspectives;
- You want to enjoy a touching story with good acting and brilliant non-linear storytelling;
- You don't mind to just sit there, type few words, click and watch videos;
